WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
What can I do for you?

00:07.000 --> 00:10.760
I'd like to buy a t-shirt for my mom.

00:10.760 --> 00:13.000
What colour does she like?

00:13.000 --> 00:14.000
Purple.

00:14.000 --> 00:16.000
Alright.

00:16.000 --> 00:19.000
What size does she take?

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
Small.

00:21.000 --> 00:24.000
What about this one?

00:24.000 --> 00:26.000
May I try it on?

00:26.000 --> 00:28.000
Certainly.

00:28.000 --> 00:31.000
Oh, look at the price.

00:31.000 --> 00:34.000
It's 198 yuan.

00:34.000 --> 00:36.000
That's too much.

00:36.000 --> 00:38.000
But wait a minute.

00:38.000 --> 00:40.000
There's a sale on today.

00:40.000 --> 00:43.000
Everything is half price.

00:43.000 --> 00:45.000
Ah, okay.

00:45.000 --> 00:48.000
I'll take it.

00:48.000 --> 00:51.000
I've got some food to buy too.

00:51.000 --> 00:53.000
Can I help you?

00:53.000 --> 00:54.000
Yes.

00:54.000 --> 00:56.000
I'd like some sausages.

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
How much are they?

00:58.000 --> 01:00.000
38 yuan a kilo.

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
How much would you like?

01:02.000 --> 01:04.000
Half a kilo.

01:04.000 --> 01:06.000
Okay.

01:06.000 --> 01:08.000
What else would you like?

01:08.000 --> 01:12.000
A kilo of beans and two lemons.

01:12.000 --> 01:15.000
That'll be 30 yuan.

01:15.000 --> 01:18.000
Oh, the strawberries look fresh.

01:18.000 --> 01:20.000
How much are they?

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
10 yuan a kilo.

01:22.000 --> 01:24.000
One kilo please.

01:24.000 --> 01:26.000
Here's 59 yuan.

